{"tid":1029907,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本月KFC逾200客食物中毒　全國分店暫停營業","createTime":"2019-02-20T14:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T14:51:48.000Z","uid":66271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"779f126a8df2957f53a6877e17005d06fb28115a","tid":1029907,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190220/photo/bkn-20190220062117259-0220_00912_001_01p.jpg?20190220062237\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190220%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190220062117259-0220_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20190220062237&h=f0a2aac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蒙古最近逾200名曾光顧肯德基（KFC）快餐店的人出現食物中毒症狀，當中數十人送院救治。當局下令境內所有KFC餐廳暫停營業。<br />\n<br />\n首宗案例於本月較早時間發生，16人進食KFC的食品後，出現包括腹瀉、嘔吐與高燒等食物中毒症狀。首都烏蘭巴托大都會專業檢驗局表示，目前已接獲247個類似個案，並有42人留醫。<br />\n<br />\n當局正調查事件起因，並決定勒令國內共11間肯德基餐廳暫停營業，它們全都設在烏蘭巴托。初步調查發現，其中一家餐廳的35名員工未經徹底審核，就獲准處理食物，當中多數人沒有接受體檢，屬於違法。<br />\n<br />\n另外KFC餐廳亦被發現衛生情況極不理想。餐廳飲用水含有毒性強的克雷伯氏菌屬，而在一部汽水機則發現微量大腸桿菌，並有4人與肯德基員工接觸後，感染會導致發燒與腹瀉的志賀氏菌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190220/bkn-20190220062117259-0220_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190220%2Fbkn-20190220062117259-0220_00912_001.html&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n84MLxsd%2B2XAbZoZSjzCx9%2B0%3D&h=0d426195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190220/bkn-20190220062117259-0220_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fa0e7e51105acd0cddd5c9e8c35dd46e4921f4bf","tid":1029907,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:44:12.000Z","msg":"大陸完全唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236739e5de073e5c9ec74f4990cd40abecdc06c1","tid":1029907,"uid":511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fa0e7e51105acd0cddd5c9e8c35dd4